QuestData.Title: You Go First
QuestData.Description:
You've proven useful. So, I am going to require you to disarm the defenses of this hall.
Please take care not to die too quickly. I'd like to have the spear before the end of this eon.
QuestData.LogDescription: Disarm the traps within the Third Chamber of Kalliope and make your way to the final hall.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Artificer Ligiea within the final hall of the Third Chamber of Kalliope.

Objectives.Objective: Disarm the first set of traps
Disarm the second set of traps
Disarm the third set of traps
